    <text x="70" y="365" fill="#71717a" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">時期未定</text>
    <text x="70" y="387" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">CFTCの公式対応期限は公表されていない</text>
    <text x="680" y="415" fill="#52525b" font-size="12" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">出典: CFTC、連邦官報、ザ・ブロック(7月9日)</text>
  </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="es">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 430" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Cronología regulatoria de la CFTC 2026 sobre derivados onchain</text>
    <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">De una carta de no acción a una carta de comentarios conjunta, en cuatro meses</text>
    <line x1="46" y1="80" x2="46" y2="390" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="2"/>
    <circle cx="46" cy="100" r="7" fill="#38bdf8"/>
    <text x="70" y="95" fill="#38bdf8" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">17 mar. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="117" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">La CFTC emite la Carta de No Acción 26-09 a Phantom —</text>
    <text x="70" y="136" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">acceso a derivados sin registro de IB, bajo condiciones</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="190" r="7" fill="#a1a1aa"/>
    <text x="70" y="185" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">18 jun. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="207" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">La CFTC publica la RFI de innovación fintech bajo la</text>
    <text x="70" y="226" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Orden Ejecutiva 14405, abriendo 21 días de comentarios</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="280" r="7" fill="#4ade80"/>
    <text x="70" y="275" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">9 jul. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="297" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Cierra el periodo; HPC y Phantom presentan carta conjunta</text>
    <text x="70" y="316" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">pidiendo confirmar la exención y crear una regla real</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="370" r="7" fill="#71717a" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>
    <text x="70" y="365" fill="#71717a" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Fecha sin fijar</text>
    <text x="70" y="387" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">La CFTC no ha dado un plazo público para responder</text>
    <text x="680" y="415" fill="#52525b" font-size="12" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">Fuente: CFTC, Registro Federal, The Block (9 jul.)</text>
  </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="de">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 430" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">CFTCs Zeitplan 2026 zu Onchain-Derivaten</text>
    <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Vom No-Action-Schreiben zum gemeinsamen Kommentarschreiben in vier Monaten</text>
    <line x1="46" y1="80" x2="46" y2="390" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="2"/>
    <circle cx="46" cy="100" r="7" fill="#38bdf8"/>
    <text x="70" y="95" fill="#38bdf8" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">17. Mär. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="117" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">CFTC erteilt Phantom das No-Action-Schreiben 26-09 —</text>
    <text x="70" y="136" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Derivatezugang ohne IB-Registrierung, unter Auflagen</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="190" r="7" fill="#a1a1aa"/>
    <text x="70" y="185" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">18. Jun. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="207" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">CFTC veröffentlicht Fintech-Innovations-RFI gemäß</text>
    <text x="70" y="226" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Executive Order 14405, 21-tägiges Kommentarfenster startet</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="280" r="7" fill="#4ade80"/>
    <text x="70" y="275" fill="#4ade80" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">9. Jul. 2026</text>
    <text x="70" y="297" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Frist endet; HPC und Phantom reichen gemeinsames</text>
    <text x="70" y="316" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">Schreiben ein — Bestätigung und feste Regel gefordert</text>
    <circle cx="46" cy="370" r="7" fill="#71717a" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>
    <text x="70" y="365" fill="#71717a" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Termin offen</text>
    <text x="70" y="387" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="14" font-family="sans-serif">CFTC nennt keine öffentliche Frist für eine Antwort</text>
    <text x="680" y="415" fill="#52525b" font-size="12" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">Quelle: CFTC, Federal Register, The Block (9. Juli)</text>
  </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="fr">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 430" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
